import React from 'react'
import './App.css'

import Nav from './components/Nav/Nav'
import Profile from './components/Profile/Profile'
import ProfileNav from './components/Profile_nav/Profile_nav'
import News from './components/News/News'
import Sidebar from './components/Sidebar/Sidebar'

export type aaa = {
  children: string
}

function App<aaa>() {
  return (
    <>
      <main className="main">
        <Nav children="tweet" />
        <section className="list">
          <Profile />
          <ProfileNav />
          <News />
          <News />
        </section>
        <Sidebar />
      </main>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
